cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you refer to this work, please cite it as below."
title: "Labour-Market Transitions & Wealth Dynamics"
abstract: >-
  Research-assistant work in empirical labour economics: harmonised individual
  panels built from the PSID, NLSY79, NLSY97 and CPS surveys to estimate
  employment / unemployment / inactivity transition rates and income & wealth
  trajectories, validated against FRED and the Fallick & Fleischman and Shimer
  benchmarks. Code, result graphs and reports only (microdata excluded).
type: software
authors:
